data.description: Check out this charming 4 bedroom 2 full bath 2 half bath with a main level owners suite on 7.62 acres! With the detached oversized garage, you can store all of your recreational activity toys for the land and for the marina that is located just at the end of this quiet road! The basement has an open concept with a fireplace, bar, and a half bath that can easily be transformed to a in law suite or for some rental income! The main level living area has beautiful built-ins surrounding the fireplace and the owners suite with a large walk in closet has plenty of storage space. The upper level host 3 generous size bedrooms and a full bath. Seller offering $5,000 closing cost assistance too!
